            "url": "https://todon.eu/@EndemicEarthling/112951727868978593",
            "replies_count": 1,
            "reblogs_count": 0,
            "favourites_count": 1,
            "edited_at": null,
            "content": "<p><span class=\"h-card\" translate=\"no\"><a href=\"https://tech.lgbt/@CriticalCupcake\" class=\"u-url mention\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">@<span>CriticalCupcake</span></a></span></p><p>Global policy priority to help stop/slow <a href=\"https://todon.eu/tags/ClimateDisruption\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>ClimateDisruption</span></a>: vigorously pursue (actual) <a href=\"https://todon.eu/tags/democracy\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>democracy</span></a> at all relevant levels and contexts.</p><p>Requires: (a) dismantling/diminution/decentralising of all de facto hyper-concentrations of power (which in practice make actually democratic processes and outcomes impossible/severely compromised);<br>(b) empowering of the billions currently impoverished and subjected by those hyper-concentrations.</p><p>Illustrative step towards each of these:<br>(a) Maximum wealth limit: 100% tax on all wealth above a certain threshold, which starts in the billions and moves down over time, with the goal of lowering the number of orders of magnitude of wealth (and power) differential between the wealthiest and the poorest;<br>(b) reallocate these resources towards nurturing cooperative/worker-owned enterprises, i.e. democracy in the workplace, along with expanding access to education, housing, healthcare, healthy food/water/air/ecosystems (i.e. establishing minimum wealth/wellbeing standards) while simultaneously embracing a variety of reforms/expansions of/experiments in growing informed democratic agency.</p><p>Ok, I might have articulated slightly more than one policy...</p>",
            "reblog": null,
            "account": {
                "id": "109385279417270100",
                "username": "EndemicEarthling",
                "acct": "EndemicEarthling@todon.eu",
                "display_name": "EndemicEarthling",
